<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates for file system creation requests in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are continuing to experience increased error rates for file system creation requests in the US-EAST-1 Region, and are actively working to resolve the issue.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates>
Between 2:40 PM and 4:45 PM PST, we experienced increased error rates for file system creation requests in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is now operating normally.
